{"tid":1186583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6月9號邊個衝邊個就係鬼...就奇呀屌！","createTime":"2019-06-05T04:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T02:57:27.000Z","uid":89170,"like":93,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d80e07ca7802eb12ad2559fd1272108178f944c2","tid":1186583,"uid":89170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:48:41.000Z","msg":"點解隔咗咁耐 都係咁多人有種邊個衝邊個係鬼嘅心態？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u831qjK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu831qjK.png&h=35f714a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明白香港嘅情況，和平遊行係吸引到多啲人參與<br />\n但你自己支持和平唔緊要<br />\n你唔好抹去打算抗爭嗰班人嘅存在<br />\n<br />\n我望住個post啲正皮，真係睇到龜頭都痛撚埋<br />\n內鬼存在完全唔出奇，但一開波就劃清界線話自己100%和平示威，唔挑起暴力衝突，有人搞事有得駁<br />\n<br />\n咁樣未開波就爭係住割蓆，喺度劃清界線<br />\n到時真係準備好反抗嘅人點算？一開始就俾人縛手縛腳，佢地咪腹背受敵？<br />\n有意外真係衝突起上嚟，到時自己友阻自己咪仲衰<br />\n<br />\n大是大非前，有想去遊行嘅人仲抱住啲和理非非能夠感化世人嘅天真諗法都唔緊要，求同存異<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但至少有人仲肯為你地而衝嘅時候，唔好第一個推佢地去死，爭住內訌得唔得？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔求你幫手衝，只求你唔好妨礙或者鬧返呢班勇士轉頭，你唔滿意咪最多倒頭走繼續你嘅和平非暴力<br />\n你有你嘅和平遊行 佢地有佢地抗爭</span><br />\n<br />\n鳩行遊行咁多年 我真係好希望今次係有成效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58a9eeacc0e014d10787dc5300ad02c9a495dde","tid":1186583,"uid":89170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:49:11.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhhhh"},{"pid":"03c91a8ebf954545d05e4e6f47671f9a8a16d754","tid":1186583,"uid":89170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:49:27.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhh"},{"pid":"6d715ab861db243fb1f3ddb43cdce05a132a7dfa","tid":1186583,"uid":3860,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:49:51.000Z","msg":"希望兄弟爬山，大家各自努力<br />\n唔好捉鬼同互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4fd9c63d0e007fca7f8e9dd43fbf2e683d0fcd8","tid":1186583,"uid":89170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6d715ab861db243fb1f3ddb43cdce05a132a7dfa","tid":1186583,"uid":3860,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:49:51.000Z","msg":"希望兄弟爬山，大家各自努力<br />\n唔好捉鬼同互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:52:10.000Z","msg":"真 唔好捉鬼同互屌<br />\n<br />\n唔幫手同幫倒忙真係差好遠"},{"pid":"138f2aeced0926048391ba3b0bb9e093c48ac07d","tid":1186583,"uid":89170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d43539b9262db56dee04731387b7ae3d022af155","tid":1186583,"uid":89170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:00:34.000Z","msg":"Too long嘅話睇紅字都好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983bae76ba9fc384f17f29cf4bd4797ec5253da4","tid":1186583,"uid":2144,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:05:41.000Z","msg":"有啲人怕餐死怕俾人秋後算帳所以先玩割𥱊，以為和理非非就可以解決問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa80b733ca36e65a064a84002d36ad6003809bc7","tid":1186583,"uid":93450,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"雨革都過左五年啦 仲邊個衝邊個係鬼<br />\n今次你再糾察篤灰 啲義士隨時要上去坐架<br />\n天安門三君子有版你睇啦"},{"pid":"384058a1a5d8b496989b6fe8f5b9558f5cd3a1ef","tid":1186583,"uid":89170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fa80b733ca36e65a064a84002d36ad6003809bc7","tid":1186583,"uid":93450,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"雨革都過左五年啦 仲邊個衝邊個係鬼<br />\n今次你再糾察篤灰 啲義士隨時要上去坐架<br />\n天安門三君子有版你睇啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:19:49.000Z","msg":"就算唔認同義士嘅做法<br />\n都唔應該阻佢地<br />\n<br />\n佢地真係用自己嘅安全嚟搏<img src